### Get all tickets
GET http://localhost:5280/api/tickets

### Get one ticket
GET http://localhost:5280/api/tickets/1

### Create a ticket
POST http://localhost:5280/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "electricity problem",
  "description": "no electricity after 7 pm on sunday",
  "category": "Electricity",
  "priority": "Urgent",
  "reportedBy": "Sara"
}

### Update ticket 1 (expect 200 + updated ticket)
PUT http://localhost:5280/api/tickets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Pothole on Main St - fixed?",
  "description": "Follow-up after repair crew visited",
  "category": "Roads",
  "priority": "Medium"
}

### Update a ticket that doesn't exist (expect 404)
PUT http://localhost:5280/api/tickets/9999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Doesn't matter",
  "description": "Doesn't matter",
  "category": "Roads",
  "priority": "Low"
}

### Delete an existing ticket (expect 204)
DELETE http://localhost:5280/api/tickets/1

### Delete a ticket that doesn't exist (expect 404)
DELETE http://localhost:5280/api/tickets/9999

### Get comments for a ticket (expect 200 + array)
GET http://localhost:5280/api/tickets/2/comments

### Get comments for a ticket that doesn't exist (expect 404)
GET http://localhost:5280/api/tickets/9999/comments

POST http://localhost:5280/api/tickets/2/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author": "Agent Lina",
  "text": "Crew dispatched, ETA 30 minutes."
}

### Add a comment to a non-existent ticket (expect 404)
POST http://localhost:5280/api/tickets/9999/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author": "Agent Lina",
  "text": "Doesn't matter"
}

### Get all categories with live ticket counts (expect 200 + array)
GET http://localhost:5280/api/categories